    <section id="section_N1001F_N1001C_N10001" id="379">
      <p id="6">The script is used to configure the first controller in the HP Helion OpenStack Carrier Grade
        cluster as <nameliteral id="370">controller-0</nameliteral> (see <xref href="jow1404333496222.xml" id="8"/>). The prompts are grouped by configuration
        area. Details for each area are described in the following tables. Review them carefully
        before committing configuration changes to the controller. For configuration planning
        information, see the <cite id="375">HP Helion OpenStack Carrier Grade System Engineering
          Guidelines</cite>.</p>
